## Summary
This documentation explains the decision between cross-platform instrumentation (using the same API key across platforms) versus per-platform instrumentation (separate API keys) in Amplitude, outlining when each approach is appropriate based on user behavior patterns and analysis goals, while recommending separate keys for test and production environments.

